Often little-noticed archetype in society: Young employee, that has to pass bad news(Backoffice?) to customer or other stakeholders. The Secretary behind the Windwos Computer apologizes verbally, non-verbally she enjoys her power (maybe her father much to "imperative"?). Further the regulated income makes her as ignorant as a cocaine consumer. (Income ⇨ Maslow::SafetyNeeds fulfilled ⇨ "self-esteem" ⇨ dopamine release ⇨ feels superior ⇨ ignorance). Relevant scenes, why Robert De Niro runs amok, running amok is a strong image that overwrites other scenes that have led the amok, but not in the subconscious of the participants: sin ⇨ compulsion ⇨ crime
